then"},{"id":"M-xjT8RZ7F-5iJQ1_7408","type":"rectangle","x":391,"y":423,"width":587,"height":150,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#000000","backgroundColor":"#82c91e","fillStyle":"hachure","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"strokeSharpness":"round","seed":1377878171,"version":138,"versionNonce":1677980181,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[{"type":"text","id":"qasv7ii2GXBZHaeYZWXzm"}],"updated":1747106843592,"link":null},{"id":"qasv7ii2GXBZHaeYZWXzm","type":"text","x":396,"y":428,"width":577,"height":140,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#000000","backgroundColor":"#fab005","fillStyle":"hachure","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"strokeSharpness":"round","seed":1269830709,"version":76,"versionNonce":1140565435,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":null,"updated":1747106843592,"link":null,"text":"    1. master has accepted all required Ethernet devices, but is not \nrequested by any application yet. \n    2. The master runs its state machine, that automatically scans \nthe bus for slaves and executes pending operations from the userspace\ninterface (for example SDO access). \n    3. The command-line tool can be used to access the bus, but there\nis no process data exchange because of the missing bus configuration.","fontSize":16,"fontFamily":1,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","baseline":134,"containerId":"M-xjT8RZ7F-5iJQ1_7408","originalText":"    1. master has accepted all required Ethernet devices, but is not requested by any application yet. \n    2. The master runs its state machine, that automatically scans the bus for slaves and executes pending operations from the userspace interface (for example SDO access). \n    3. The command-line tool can be used to access the bus, but there is no process data exchange because of the missing bus configuration."},{"id":"PUNOkPAszNwxQs5upERPk","type":"rectangle","x":1019,"y":46,"width":267,"height":128,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#000000","backgroun